.entry-header
Established in 2001
Williston Crossings is located between Gainesville and Ocala in North Central Florida
situated on
135 acres. Our resort has 436 spacious RV sites, each with concrete pads, pull through or back in sites, and wide paved roads. Every site is equipped with full-service amenities,
free cable TV & Internet. Upgraded internet available.
We look forward to your stay.
Staff and Managment
